nodes.body: This turned out to require non-trivial changes, so I have removed `auto-merge-after-CI`.

This PR has some failures in `Mathlib.Computability.Primrec`, arising because the definition of `List.indexOf` has changed (the `==` test has flipped).

I'm not familiar with this file. It looks like @digama0 is listed as the author, and @prakol16 did the port. Might either of you be able to take a look at the failures in that file?
